name: Shredded Cave (diptych - panel B)
description:
DefCol02-0012 - 3D geometry generated and deformed in Processing, rendered in Rhino and color manipulated. 
Edition of 5+1 AP, 2022, Marius Watz @mariuswatz

Diptych - each panel is a 4000x6000px PNG. Only panel A will be listed for sale, buyers will have panel B airdropped to their wallet. Any resale should include both panels, splitting the piece is against the artist's intentions.
